body:
### What steps will reproduce the problem?
I've got the following configuration of cache driver:
```php
return [
    'id' => 'app',
    'basePath' => dirname(__DIR__),
    'bootstrap' => ['log'],
    'language' => 'en-US',
    'components' => [
        'cache' => function () {
            $cfg = ArrayHelper::getValue(App::getConfig(), 'app.cache');
            if (!is_array($cfg)) {
                throw new InvalidConfigException('Invalid cache configuration.');
            }
            $cfg['keyPrefix'] = 'it_does_not_matter';
            return Yii::createObject($cfg);
        }
       // other modules
    ]
];
```
Because definition is Closure [CacheController](https://github.com/yiisoft/yii2/blob/master/framework/console/controllers/CacheController.php) this component doesn't find a driver.
I run the following command:
`./yii cache`
### What is the expected result?
```text
The following caches were found in the system:

	* cache (yii\caching\FileCache)
```

### What do you get instead?
```text
No cache components were found in the system.
```
### Additional info
I propose change this method [findCaches](https://github.com/yiisoft/yii2/blob/master/framework/console/controllers/CacheController.php#L252) to following:
```php
/**
     * Returns array of caches in the system, keys are cache components names, values are class names.
     * @param array $cachesNames caches to be found
     * @return array
     */
    private function findCaches(array $cachesNames = [])
    {
        $caches = [];
        $components = Yii::$app->getComponents();
        $findAll = ($cachesNames === []);

        foreach ($components as $name => $component) {
            if (!$findAll && !in_array($name, $cachesNames)) {
                continue;
            }

            if ($component instanceof Cache) {
                $caches[$name] = get_class($component);
            } elseif (is_array($component) && isset($component['class']) && $this->isCacheClass($component['class'])) {
                $caches[$name] = $component['class'];
            } elseif (is_string($component) && $this->isCacheClass($component)) {
                $caches[$name] = $component;
            } elseif (is_callable($component) && $this->isCacheClass(Yii::$app->get($name, false))) {
                $caches[$name] = get_class(Yii::$app->get($name));
            }
        }

        return $caches;
    }
```

| Q                | A
| ---------------- | ---
| Yii version      | 2.0.11.2
| PHP version      | 5.4.45
| Operating system | Ubuntu
